These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-1::.
There 3 different types of food: cherry, carrot, grapes
The people have 3 different jobs:  nurse, entrepreneur, coach
1. the person eating cherry is in an even position##4
2. the nurse is on the left or right of the coach##3
3. the nurse is the person eating carrot##1
4. the person eating grapes is on the far left##1
5. the entrepreneur is the entrepreneur##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Food   | grapes | cherry | carrot |
| Job    | entrepreneur    | coach | nurse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: hiking, rock-climbing, writing
The people use 3 different means of transport: snowmobile, airplane, subway
1. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the airplane is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
4. the person driving the airplane is the person driving the airplane##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Hobby       | rock-climbing | writing | hiking |
| Transport   | subway    | airplane     | snowmobile        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, hiking, card-games
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: hip-hop, folk, country
1. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
2. the fan of folk is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3    |
| Hobby         | card-games     | hiking | camping |
| Music-Genre   | folk | hip-hop     | country  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: mystery, crime, martial-arts
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: weightlifting, handball, badminton
1. the person watching crime movies is the person who's sport is handball##1
2. the person watching mystery movies is the person who's sport is badminton##1
3. the person watching crime movies is in an even position##4
4. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | crime  | mystery  |
| Sport         | weightlifting  | handball | badminton |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, puzzles, dancing
There are 3 different nationalities: indian, malaysian, american
1. the person who's hobby is dancing is between the person who's hobby is baking and the indian##2
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is in an odd position##4
3. the american is on the left of the indian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Hobby         | baking   | dancing | puzzles    |
| Nationality   | malaysian | american     | indian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-6::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, traveling, dancing
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, baseball, golf
1. the person who's hobby is chess is the person who's sport is baseball##1
2. the person who's sport is golf is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
3. the person who's hobby is traveling is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Hobby   | traveling | dancing | chess   |
| Sport   | golf     | biathlon    | baseball |

