.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: western, superhero, zombie
3 different pets are kept: horse, pony, rabbit
1. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
2. the person watching western movies is between the owner of the rabbit and the person watching zombie movies##2
3. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
4. the owner of the horse is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | western | superhero |
| Pet           | pony         | horse         | rabbit |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-8::.
There 3 different types of food: pineapple, lemon, strawberry
3 different pets are kept: cat, hedgehog, pony
1. the owner of the cat is between the owner of the hedgehog and the person eating pineapple##2
2. the owner of the pony is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |     3     |
| Food   | lemon | strawberry | pineapple |
| Pet    | hedgehog    | cat | pony     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-9::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: electronic, folk, blues
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rugby, baseball, golf
1. the person who's sport is golf is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
3. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the fan of folk##1
4. the person who's sport is golf is on the left or right of the person who's sport is baseball##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Music-Genre   | blues   | folk  | electronic  |
| Sport         | golf | baseball | rugby |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, lemonade, iced-tea
There 3 different types of food: banana, lemon, kiwi
1. the person eating banana is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the person eating kiwi is in an even position##4
3. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage   | water    | iced-tea      | lemonade |
| Food       | lemon | kiwi | banana   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-11::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  project-manager, coach, nurse
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, skateboard, jet-ski
1. the nurse is on the right of the coach##1
2. the person driving the bike is the project-manager##1
3. the person driving the jet-ski is the nurse##1
4. the nurse is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |     3      |
| Job         | coach | nurse | project-manager |
| Transport   | skateboard | jet-ski   | bike |

