2. the polish is the person driving the bus##1
3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the thai##3
4. the person driving the bus is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |
| Nationality   | argentine | thai | polish |
| Transport     | quad-bike     | ship   | bus        |

