.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-13::.
There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, german, japanese
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: volleyball, climbing, biathlon
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the japanese##1
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is the german##1
3. the japanese is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
