.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-14::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: woodworking, magic-tricks, fishing
3 different pets are kept: goat, horse, snake
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the owner of the horse##2
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the horse is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks | fishing | woodworking |
| Pet     | goat    | snake  | horse   |

