2. the fan of funk is on the left of the fan of classical##1
3. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the person watching epic movies##3
4. the person watching epic movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure  | epic     | fantasy |
| Music-Genre   | funk | classical | pop    |

