.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-18::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: filmmaking, rock-climbing, magic-tricks
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: country, trance, ambient
1. the fan of ambient is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is in the middle##1
3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the fan of trance##1
4. the fan of country is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | filmmaking   | rock-climbing |
| Music-Genre   | trance   | country | ambient      |

