.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-19::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, cola, water
There are 3 different nationalities: chinese, mexican, japanese
1. the japanese is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
2. the person drinking iced-tea is in an odd position##4
3. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
4. the person drinking cola is on the left of the chinese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |    3     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | cola | water |
| Nationality   | mexican   | japanese          | chinese |

