.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-20::.
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, cat, frog
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, snowboarding, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
3. the owner of the frog is in an even position##4
4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the owner of the cat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3      |
| Pet     | cat  | frog   | hedgehog |
| Sport   | weightlifting | snowboarding | cricket       |

 